      .col-md-3
        .thumbnail
          .caption
            h3.center ss-hogan
            p Use pre-compiled Hogan (Mustache-compatible) client-side templates in your app to benefit from increased performance and a smaller client-side library download.
    a(href="https://github.com/socketstream/ss-coffeekup")
      .col-md-3
        .thumbnail
          .caption
            h3.center ss-coffeekup
